title: General Electric Rises 7%
text:
Investing.com - General Electric (NYSE:GE) rose by 7.41% to trade at $9.71 by 09:30 (13:30 GMT) on Wednesday on the NYSE exchange.

The volume of General Electric shares traded since the start of the session was 26.16M. General Electric has traded in a range of $9.71 to $9.85 on the day.

The stock has traded at $9.8000 at its highest and $8.6100 at its lowest during the past seven days.
